Description:
   Ashfall Strike is a debilitating combat technique used by experienced Wardens.
   The warrior delivers a powerful blow that leaves a residual ash-like coating on
   the target, reducing their combat effectiveness. The strike applies a stacking
   debuff that lowers the target's armor class and attack rolls for a short
   duration.

   Each application of Ashfall Strike refreshes and intensifies the debuff,
   making it valuable to apply repeatedly in extended fights. The effect is
   particularly potent against heavily armored foes, as the ashen coating
   interferes with joint articulation and visibility.
